The paper discusses a method for ranking key phrases in documents based on semantic role information and sentence position. This involves natural language processing and information retrieval techniques, which are commonly associated with the sub-categories of Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
